{\bf Double-precision version:}
\begin{verbatim}
    CALL DMINFC(F,A,B,EPS,DELTA,X,Y,LRM)
\end{verbatim}
where {\tt F}, {\tt A}, {\tt B}, {\tt EPS}, {\tt DELTA}, {\tt X}
and {\tt Y} are of type {\tt DOUBLE PRECISION}.
